🎨Meet, Paint & Connect! 🤝

Ready to get creative? Join us for a fun evening of painting, meeting new people, and chatting with your Execs—plus, enjoy some free pizza while you’re at it!

⏰ Time: 5:30 PM - 8:00 PM

Link in bio—Get your spots before it’s too late!
